title: SPY HAPPY HOUR JUNE 19TH 2015 w/ MMX & KARMIC HEALTH
description: SPY CEO and President Michael Marckx awards the Sultan of Stoke, Aidan Runner, the SPY high five and goes on to explore the nature of innate optimism. Following Michael, Sandy Star of Karmic Health encourages SPY employees to create a new sense of self wellness by turning to optimal foods.
